snippet.title: Journey Beyond the Edge of the World (Game Teaser)
snippet.description:
Journey Beyond the Edge of the World, an atmospheric first person adventure game in which you solve puzzles to unfold a mysterious and surreal story. A story told in a unique way through 5 narrated music tracks.

🔍 Explore a storm-torn ship
⚙️ Solve item-based puzzles to unlock ...
📻 ... 5 narrated ambient music tracks telling the story
🎧 Experience #SpatialAudio!

Wishlist on Steam: https://wishlist.journeybeyondthegame.com
Join the Discord: https://discord.com/invite/y4WKmbRD9c
Follow on Social Media: www.journeybeyondthegame.com
